From: Grzegorz Jaszczyk <jaz@semihalf.com>
Date: Wed, 25 Apr 2018 16:32:49 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 0600/1051] arm64: dts: marvell: 7040-db: add comphy references
 to USB ports

Adding phandle to the USB port will allow HCD driver to configure
appropriate marvell, comphy-cp110 accordingly.

Change-Id: I3a1ec6f40bc0b4c826ec81f01fcc2df881e07feb
Signed-off-by: Grzegorz Jaszczyk <jaz@semihalf.com>
[Kevin: The original patch got from Marvell sdk10.0_19.06]
Signed-off-by: Kevin Hao <kexin.hao@windriver.com>
---
 arch/arm64/boot/dts/marvell/armada-7040-db.dts | 6 ++++++
 1 file changed, 6 insertions(+)

diff --git a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/marvell/armada-7040-db.dts b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/marvell/armada-7040-db.dts
index 2e0c5a55ed70..3c0c889fcaf0 100644
--- a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/marvell/armada-7040-db.dts
+++ b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/marvell/armada-7040-db.dts
@@ -204,11 +204,17 @@
 &cp0_usb3_0 {
 	usb-phy = <&cp0_usb3_0_phy>;
 	status = "okay";
+	/* Generic PHY, providing serdes lanes */
+	phys = <&cp0_comphy1 0>;
+	phy-names = "usb";
 };
 
 &cp0_usb3_1 {
 	usb-phy = <&cp0_usb3_1_phy>;
 	status = "okay";
+	/* Generic PHY, providing serdes lanes */
+	phys = <&cp0_comphy4 1>;
+	phy-names = "usb";
 };
 
 &ap_sdhci0 {
